VDR Plugin 'ddci' Revision History
----------------------------------

2011-12-26: Version 0.0.1

- Initial revision.

2012-01-18: Version 0.0.1b

- open sec-device in non-blocking mode
- increase TS buffers to 4MB
- remove double call of Start()
- add some Makefile improvements

2012-01-22: Version 0.0.1c

- open sec two times (WRONLY and RDONLY)
- remove one thread in chain dvr->sec->vdr
